717
01:23:48,050 --> 01:23:50,310
知不知道我找你多久了?
I've been looking all over for you.

718
01:23:51,150 --> 01:23:53,750
你躲起来没有用啊
What's the point of hiding?

719
01:23:53,920 --> 01:23:56,410
要面对现实才行
You have to face reality.

720
01:23:59,360 --> 01:24:01,490
哇噻  发霉了
You're all moldy.

721
01:24:02,660 --> 01:24:05,890
明天吧
Tell you what. I'm not busy tomorrow.

722
01:24:06,230 --> 01:24:08,360
明天我有空带你晒太阳
I'll take you out for some sun.

723
01:24:54,680 --> 01:24:56,310
你怎么会在我家里啊?
What are you doing in my apartment?

724
01:24:56,480 --> 01:24:58,710
不是你叫我有空到你家来坐的吗?
You said to drop by!

725
01:25:01,320 --> 01:25:05,160
快开门啊  不然我撞门了啊
Open up or I'll break the door down!

726
01:25:36,060 --> 01:25:38,720
喂  有人找你啊
There's someone looking for you.

727
01:25:38,890 --> 01:25:40,520
- 找我?  - 是啊
- Me? - Yeah.

728
01:25:46,170 --> 01:25:49,400
- 你怎么会在这儿?  - 我来拿封信
- What do you want? - I've come for my letter.

729
01:25:49,570 --> 01:25:51,660
什么信啊?  你问老板啊
What letter? Ask the boss.

730
01:25:52,570 --> 01:25:55,130
问我干嘛?  在你那儿嘛
You were keeping it.

731
01:25:55,310 --> 01:25:57,040
老板说在你那儿
He said you had it.

732
01:25:57,210 --> 01:25:58,440
在我这儿?
I do?

733
01:26:00,580 --> 01:26:02,070
在我这儿吗?
I have it?

734
01:26:02,250 --> 01:26:03,880
对了
Oh, right.

735
01:26:07,760 --> 01:26:11,120
我怕丢了  我帮你收起来了  我没有看过啊
I was afraid someone might take it. I didn't read it.

736
01:26:15,930 --> 01:26:16,990
谢谢你啊
Thanks.

737
01:26:19,430 --> 01:26:21,870
明天晚上有没有空?
Are you free tomorrow night?

738
01:26:22,100 --> 01:26:24,000
干嘛问我明天晚上有没有空?
Why do you ask?

739
01:26:24,170 --> 01:26:26,470
- 想约你出去  - 干嘛约我出去?
- I want to ask you out. - On a date?

740
01:26:26,640 --> 01:26:29,070
老板说你明天晚上不用上班
The boss says you're off tomorrow.

741
01:26:30,310 --> 01:26:32,970
不上班就得跟你出去啊?
So I have to go on a date?

742
01:26:33,150 --> 01:26:35,010
你考虑一下
Think it over.

743
01:26:35,180 --> 01:26:39,950
明天晚上八点  在对面那家"加州"等你
I'll meet you across the street at the California at 8:00.

744
01:26:42,360 --> 01:26:44,920
这首歌不适合你听
That music's not your style.

745
01:26:45,090 --> 01:26:46,890
听这首
Listen to this.

746
01:26:59,770 --> 01:27:01,540
完了  完了
Damn it!

747
01:27:02,780 --> 01:27:05,540
完了  完了  完了
Damn it, damn it, damn it!

748
01:27:09,480 --> 01:27:11,710
喂  663泡妞真有一套啊
No. 663 is a smooth operator.

749
01:27:11,890 --> 01:27:14,820
- 老板  你要学学663  - 神经病
- It's 663. - Whatever it is!

750
01:27:20,660 --> 01:27:23,060
稍等
Wait!

751
01:27:26,460 --> 01:27:30,330
- 加酱汁吗?  - 好的
- Chilli sauce? - Okay.

752
01:27:35,110 --> 01:27:37,510
- 我的可乐呢?  - 可乐  没有杯子啊
- Where's my Coke? - I'm out of cups!

753
01:27:47,760 --> 01:27:50,620
那天下午我在家里大扫除
I gave my place a thorough cleaning that afternoon.

754
01:27:50,790 --> 01:27:54,660
我好像在清理跑道  准备第二架飞机降落
It was like clearing the runway for another plane to land.

755
01:28:33,970 --> 01:28:36,460
那天晚上我早就到了"加州"
I got to the California really early that night.

756
01:28:36,640 --> 01:28:38,800
因为我不知道飞机会不会Delay
I half expected a flight delay,

757
01:28:38,970 --> 01:28:41,240
我换了十块钱零钱
so I got some loose change.

758
01:28:53,590 --> 01:28:54,680
喂  麻烦你帮我换零钱
Change, please.

759
01:29:13,740 --> 01:29:17,040
半个钟头后  我又换了十块钱零钱
Half an hour later, I broke another $10 bill.

760
01:29:17,980 --> 01:29:20,910
我开始有预感那班飞机已经Cancel了
I started thinking maybe the flight was canceled.

761
01:29:44,440 --> 01:29:46,200
她不会来了
She isn't coming.

762
01:29:46,370 --> 01:29:49,100
她叫我把这封信交给你
She asked me to give you this.

763
01:29:51,510 --> 01:29:53,710
用不着那么失望
Don't look so down.

764
01:29:53,880 --> 01:29:57,010
泡不上她  可以泡别人嘛  对不对?
She didn't work out, so try another girl.

765
01:29:57,180 --> 01:30:00,980
阿May明天又回来做了  泡阿May吧
May's coming back tomorrow. Give her a try.

766
01:30:01,490 --> 01:30:04,510
- 她人呢?  - 她辞职了
- Where is she? - She quit.

767
01:30:04,690 --> 01:30:06,920
她说去什么  加州什么的
Said she was going to California.

768
01:30:08,060 --> 01:30:09,390
我走了
That's all.

769
01:30:09,800 --> 01:30:11,160
谢谢
Thanks.

770
01:30:16,000 --> 01:30:18,160
我没看那封信
I didn't read the letter.

771
01:30:19,040 --> 01:30:21,770
因为有些事情需要时间去接受
Some things take time to sink in.

772
01:30:22,180 --> 01:30:24,640
老板走了之后
After the snack-bar manager left,

773
01:30:24,810 --> 01:30:27,140
我开始跟啤酒瓶讲话
I started talking to the beer bottles.

774
01:30:27,780 --> 01:30:29,510
你失望了?
Disappointed?

775
01:30:30,150 --> 01:30:31,850
不会啊
Not really.

776
01:30:32,390 --> 01:30:36,080
回家睡觉吧  她不会来了
Go home to bed. She's not coming.

777
01:30:47,000 --> 01:30:48,900
其实她不是没有来
Actually, she wasn't a no-show that night.

778
01:30:49,070 --> 01:30:51,260
只是走错了地方
She just got the place wrong.

779
01:30:51,970 --> 01:30:54,100
那天晚上我们大家都在加州
We were in different Californias

780
01:30:54,640 --> 01:30:57,370
只不过我们之间相差了15个钟头
15 hours apart.

781
01:30:58,350 --> 01:31:01,870
现在是她那边早上11点
It must be 11:00 a. m. over there now.

782
01:31:03,050 --> 01:31:06,610
不知道今天晚上8点  她会不会记得约了我呢
I wonder if she'll remember our 8:00 p. m. date here.

783
01:31:20,560 --> 01:31:21,960
嗨
Hi.

784
01:31:23,500 --> 01:31:25,170
这么巧啊
What a coincidence!

785
01:31:28,040 --> 01:31:29,800
不用值班啊?
Not on duty tonight?

786
01:31:30,080 --> 01:31:31,640
放假
That's right.

787
01:31:33,250 --> 01:31:34,870
你好吗?
How are you?

788
01:31:35,180 --> 01:31:37,310
还不错  你呢?
Fine. And you?

789
01:31:37,720 --> 01:31:39,020
很好啊
I'm okay.

790
01:31:40,520 --> 01:31:41,920
一个人?
You alone?

791
01:31:42,160 --> 01:31:45,120
不是  跟朋友
No, I'm with a friend.

792
01:31:47,160 --> 01:31:48,790
很配啊
He's your type.

793
01:31:49,630 --> 01:31:52,220
你还有东西在我家里
You still have stuff at my place.

794
01:31:52,630 --> 01:31:54,030
有空上来拿吧
Come get it sometime.

795
01:31:54,600 --> 01:31:57,500
我不要了  帮我丢掉了吧
That's all right. Just throw it out.

796
01:32:00,210 --> 01:32:01,730
好
All right.

797
01:32:05,650 --> 01:32:07,240
我要走了
I gotta go.

798
01:32:10,080 --> 01:32:12,920
我还是比较想看你穿制服
I still think you look better in uniform.

799
01:32:13,090 --> 01:32:14,380
你也是
So do you.

800
01:32:15,000 --> 01:32:15,950
- 拜  - 拜
- Bye. - Bye.

801
01:32:18,660 --> 01:32:20,220
哎  你买了东西  还没给钱呐
Hey, you didn't pay.

802
01:32:20,390 --> 01:32:21,660
你帮我给吧
You pay for me.

803
01:32:52,990 --> 01:32:54,960
- 多少钱?  谢谢  - 262元
- How much is it? - $262

804
01:33:04,630 --> 01:33:05,750
谢谢
Thanks.

805
01:34:37,300 --> 01:34:41,560
那天晚上我收到一张登机证  时间是一年以后
The letter turned out to be a boarding pass dated for one year later,

806
01:34:42,070 --> 01:34:46,270
至于地点我一直没有看清楚
but I couldn't make out the destination.

807
01:34:48,230 --> 01:34:50,220
[经济位  663先生]

808
01:34:58,320 --> 01:35:00,910
其实那天我去了
I actually did show up that evening.

809
01:35:01,090 --> 01:35:04,680
我知道八点的时候人多  我七点一刻就到了
I knew it would get crowded, so I got there at 7:15.

810
01:35:05,660 --> 01:35:07,890
那天的雨特大
It was pouring outside.

811
01:35:08,060 --> 01:35:12,430
看着窗户外边  我看见了下雨的加州
Watching through the window, I saw a rainy California.

812
01:35:13,570 --> 01:35:17,230
我特想知道  另外一个加州是否阳光明媚?
I needed to know if the other California was warm and sunny.

813
01:35:17,500 --> 01:35:19,870
所以我给了自己一年的时间
I decided to give myself one year.

814
01:35:22,310 --> 01:35:25,280
今天和那天一样那么大雨
Tonight it's raining as hard as it was then.

815
01:35:25,680 --> 01:35:27,580
望着窗户外边儿
Looking out this window,

816
01:35:27,750 --> 01:35:30,150
我只是想着一个人
there's just one person in my thoughts.

817
01:35:31,650 --> 01:35:34,210
不知道他到底打开那封信没有?
I wonder if he ever opened my letter.

818
01:36:30,180 --> 01:36:32,040
你怎么会在这儿啊?
What are you doing here?

819
01:36:36,220 --> 01:36:38,650
喂  你怎么会在这儿?
Hey! What are you doing here?

820
01:36:39,350 --> 01:36:40,610
怎么是你啊?
Is that really you?

821
01:36:41,220 --> 01:36:43,710
你干嘛?
Yeah. What are you doing here?

822
01:36:43,890 --> 01:36:45,120
装修啊
Renovating.

823
01:36:45,590 --> 01:36:47,180
装修?
Renovating?

824
01:36:48,090 --> 01:36:49,720
我表哥呢?
Where's my cousin?

825
01:36:50,700 --> 01:36:52,670
你表哥开卡拉OK了
He opened a karaoke bar.

826
01:36:54,770 --> 01:36:56,740
他说想换换口味
Said he needed a change.

827
01:36:56,900 --> 01:37:00,000
所以让给我了  他没告诉你吗?
He let me take over here. Didn't he tell you?

828
01:37:00,740 --> 01:37:03,470
没有啊  好久没见他了
No, I haven't seen him.

829
01:37:03,740 --> 01:37:06,080
你表哥真会做生意
He's a shrewd businessman.

830
01:37:07,150 --> 01:37:09,620
刚开始介绍我买炸鱼薯条
First he sells me fish and chips,

831
01:37:09,780 --> 01:37:11,310
现在连店都让给我了
and then the whole shop.

832
01:37:11,480 --> 01:37:12,880
什么?
What?

833
01:37:13,390 --> 01:37:16,120
我说  你表哥很会做生意
I said your cousin is a shrewd businessman!

834
01:37:21,530 --> 01:37:24,330
你什么时候喜欢听这么闹的音乐呀?
Since when do you like this loud music?

835
01:37:26,400 --> 01:37:29,230
花点时间  适应一下就行了
With a little time, I get used to things.

836
01:37:31,000 --> 01:37:33,870
- 你不是去加州了吗?  好不好玩?  - 啊?
- Did you go to California? Was it fun? - What?

837
01:37:43,180 --> 01:37:46,180
你不是去加州了吗?  好不好玩?
Did you go to California? Was it fun?

838
01:37:46,790 --> 01:37:48,650
加州
California ...

839
01:37:49,060 --> 01:37:51,520
就那么回事  没什么特别的
was okay. Nothing special.

840
01:37:58,530 --> 01:38:00,970
你穿制服很好看
You look good in uniform.

841
01:38:02,000 --> 01:38:04,400
你这身也不赖啊
You look nice like that too.

842
01:38:04,770 --> 01:38:06,530
吃不吃东西?
Want something to eat?

843
01:38:06,770 --> 01:38:08,400
不吃了
I better not.

844
01:38:09,740 --> 01:38:12,110
明儿一早我还得飞呢
I fly out real early tomorrow.

845
01:38:14,410 --> 01:38:16,440
什么时候回来?
When will you be back?

846
01:38:16,880 --> 01:38:19,410
这里过两天就开幕了
My grand opening is in two days.

847
01:38:21,290 --> 01:38:22,780
不知道
I don't know.

848
01:38:23,290 --> 01:38:26,260
我这次可能得飞挺久的
This might be a long trip.

849
01:38:29,630 --> 01:38:32,100
到了外国写封信回来嘛?
Write to me when you reach wherever it is.

850
01:38:34,970 --> 01:38:37,230
写了你也不会看啊
You probably wouldn't read it anyway.

851
01:38:39,250 --> 01:38:42,170
哎  有个事想问你
I have to ask you something.

852
01:38:52,820 --> 01:38:54,810
如果有人给你这样的登机证
Would you let someone board

853
01:38:54,990 --> 01:38:57,010
你会不会让他上飞机?
with a boarding pass like this?

854
01:39:01,930 --> 01:39:04,830
日子是今天  可惜弄湿了
It's dated today, but it got blurred in the rain.

855
01:39:07,570 --> 01:39:10,400
又不知道去哪儿的  你知不知道?
where it's taking me. Do you know?

856
01:39:12,340 --> 01:39:13,830
不知道
No ...

857
01:39:15,480 --> 01:39:17,670
要不然给你换一张吧
but I'll give you another one.

858
01:39:21,610 --> 01:39:23,080
好啊
Great.

859
01:39:33,530 --> 01:39:35,490
你想上哪儿啊?
Where do you want to go?

860
01:39:36,730 --> 01:39:40,500
随便啊  你说去哪儿就去哪儿
Doesn't matter. Wherever you want to take me.

